sentences: Bruce Rowland (born 9 May 1942 in Melbourne) is an Australian composer.

He composed the soundtrack for the 1982 movie The Man from Snowy River, as well as the soundtrack for its 1988 sequel The Man from Snowy River II (which has the United States title of Return to Snowy River, and the United Kingdom title of The Untamed).
